{"tid":1298423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國批准對台售武　總值22億美元  108輛M1A2主戰坦克","createTime":"2019-07-09T01:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T04:22:58.000Z","uid":227801,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f184481c8629932be1f6d6ae8a5276ea5ea82bc5","tid":1298423,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:16:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467329-20190709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467329-20190709.htm&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0djKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=c3c8d4f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1467329-20190709.htm&h=06585ede\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1467329-20190709.htm</a><br />\n美國國防部表示，國務院已經批准向台灣出售108輛M1A2主戰坦克和250枚「刺針」式可擕式防空導彈系統，以及相關的系統設備，合約價值總額22億美元。<br />\n<br />\n國防部安全合作局表示，出售武器是應台灣方面的要求，認為不會改變地區的基本軍事平衡。<br />\n<br />\n美國的做法，相信會遭到北京強烈批評。大陸外交部上月曾表示，中方堅決反對美售台武器，以免嚴重損害中美關係和台海的和平穩定。"},{"pid":"7b9d415e9afc26af2917bc71f4fba6057bbb09e9","tid":1298423,"uid":209248,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港大把錢幾時賣比我地"},{"pid":"186c3c904449308e152b8424a2eb49b2f7dfc93f","tid":1298423,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c48411b762efb70591ba0a4b0a91054d519f83b","tid":1298423,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T01:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5ad0f72a310fa90f81965b0f5d5fbf65aaa2ca","tid":1298423,"uid":49588,"li